As part of efforts to sustain peaceful coexistence between the two faiths in Yobe State, the followers of Sheikh Ibrahim El-Zakzaky today for Sallah lunch at the Nasurul Mahdi Sharfuddeen Conference hall, Fudiyya Islamic Center, Potiskum town of Yobe State. Reverend Garba Sarki, of the Cocin Centre Potiskum and the Youth Leader, Malam Bala Afuwa in his remarks said that they would continue to promote peace and unity among the people.